        <title type="html"><![CDATA[我走过的杭州景区（二）]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.xuejian.site/post/wo-zou-guo-de-hang-zhou-jing-qu-er/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.xuejian.site/post/wo-zou-guo-de-hang-zhou-jing-qu-er/">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-08-21T10:57:51.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>上一篇：<a href="https://blog.xuejian.site/post/wo-zou-guo-de-hang-zhou-jing-qu-yi/" title="我走过的杭州景区（一）">我走过的杭州景区（一）</a></p>
<p><font size=4> <strong>一、曲院荷风</strong></p>
<p><font size=3>曲院荷风位于岳庙前面，无轨道交通，坐车可于岳王庙站或杭州花圃下车，交通还算便利。</p>
<p><font size=3>今天的下车处，大名鼎鼎的岳王庙，虽天气炎热，但依然忙碌依旧。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1807/65bdafc449837ef9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>入内后，荷花朵朵，甚是喜人</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1807/e3006c136eac50f0.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>荷花近照</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1807/2e2ebbe8ef5a11ad.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3> 一张图片，包含着荷花从含苞待放到花落结蓬的过程</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1807/bcac5f2d8be0683a.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3> 不知为何，石坊处的花大多还未盛开</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1807/3b24b3748f80cbf2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3> 西湖一侧的莲花皆随着太阳向外转向，有一种不愿理人的傲娇</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1807/3b8f18b586b7bc15.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=4> <strong>二、花港观鱼</strong></p>
<p><font size=3>花港观鱼是由花、港、鱼为特色的风景点,地处苏堤南段西侧，与雷峰塔、净慈寺隔苏堤相望。</p>
<p><font size=3>由苏堤上的东门入，便可看到茅盾先生所书“花港观鱼”四字牌匾</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/550ddfb624c1367c.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>入内后，右手边便是清康熙帝亲笔所题的御碑亭。这个御碑可是历史上有名的错字碑，上面的“鱼”字繁体少了一个点。相传康熙帝信佛，不忍让鱼在火上烤（因为四点是火的意思），故少书了一点</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/9a0a6c9c3f7531e9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>初秋，白莲虽未落尽，但莲蓬已经显现</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="9"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/a349dd31916ac595.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>园中题字，虽历经风霜缺依旧可辩</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="10"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/3750a1fea651533d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>关于，虽未见成群红鱼，但观小鱼嬉戏也是极好的</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="11"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/5460aa6ffbbd76aa.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>由南门出，杨公堤上，只见雷峰塔上乌云滚滚，莫不是白娘子要破塔而出</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="12"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/651a2eed06307f98.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=4> <strong>三、中国美院象山校区</strong></p>
<p><font size=3>中国美术学院象山校区位于杭州转塘镇，周围青山绿水环绕，甚是优美。</p>
<p><font size=3>学校中的标语，永远是那么的年轻，令人羡慕</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="13"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522141737.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>校园里的向日葵，开得正盛，令人羡慕</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="14"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522141803.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="15"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522141850.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="16"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522141926.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>这个作业，真的是别出声面</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="17"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/8811bf775bce5642.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>满屋的爬山虎，让人有一种绿野仙踪的感觉</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="18"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522142000.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>是不是每个校园里都有历史的印记</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="19"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522142024.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>艺术类院校，连会客展厅都如此有特色</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="20"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/IMG_20180902_142052.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=4> <strong>四、九溪十八涧</strong></p>
<p><font size=3>初秋雨后，午后的天气尚且有些炎热，但九溪内却清风徐徐。本次由龙井村出发，由南向北，经之江路九溪公交站出，据手环统计，约6到7公里，耗时约两小时。</p>
<p><font size=3>龙井村入口处有一石碑，上书“龙井村”三个大字，表明其为龙井村和九溪的分界处，由此处往南，便进入了九溪的地界。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="21"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/22cf495cd46ddce6.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>路遇小溪中湍急的水流，在群石中缠绕</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="22"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/d0b70936b48f1acc.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>一路走去，溪流总是变换着模样，以为这样我们便不认识他了</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="23"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/03f5f7466d282d98.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="24"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/344750cfe706d1ec.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>远处的小桥上有一人静坐，似乎近处的喧嚣不在，只留下安闲自得</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="25"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/fa2283f558a039df.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>走至九溪中段，有一水塘，在青山绿叶的映衬下，似有九寨沟的湖泊镜像</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="26"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/636f2a1c69937668.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="27"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/7b27c68cb0d658e3.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=4> <strong>五、太子湾公园</strong></p>
<p><font size=3>太子湾公园位于西湖西南隅，南屏山荔枝峰下。据载南宋皇室庄文、景献两太子葬此而得名。</p>
<p><font size=3>春日的太子湾公园，百花争艳，竞相开放</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="28"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1904/2ac1e54c7ce14289.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="29"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1904/2f146eaa53d16f34.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="30"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1904/a93b84a91154bf8e.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>秋日的太子湾公园虽不如春日那样百花争艳，但美丽的花朵却还是少不了的。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="31"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/c9e79fdc6057d77c.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>秋日的公园小路上，五彩缤纷。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="32"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/67ba2de7ecf7aec5.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="33"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/99278c5ee1466ce2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>虽然凛冬将至，但不畏风霜的草地却依然如春天一般，在落叶枯木的映衬下，更显得顽强。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="34"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/844c2f4befcc5ae1.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="35"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/3530eaba5463e3cd.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>同样顽强的，还有树上的它</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="36"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/3b9eac4ffd02d8df.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>偶遇风车下搞活动的学生，看着他们热热闹闹，对学生时期的生活无比怀念。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="37"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/8a80acad32177b8d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p><font size=3>秋日的太子湾公园，终于不再是游人如织，可以好好看一看公园内的景。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="38"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/624277db018d43b9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="39"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/5606855296fd2311.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="40"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1812/533ba9438b5d09ef.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    <entry>
        <title type="html"><![CDATA[我走过的杭州景区（一)]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.xuejian.site/post/wo-zou-guo-de-hang-zhou-jing-qu-yi/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.xuejian.site/post/wo-zou-guo-de-hang-zhou-jing-qu-yi/">
        </link>
        <updated>2019-08-15T10:06:55.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>一、西湖，杭州的代名词，不同时候的西湖，犹如不同打扮的西子</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>冬日清晨的断桥<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/d22b81cea53705cc.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>雨夜的断桥，人依旧那么多<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/3726da19a9c1d1a0.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>夜色来临的西湖<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/e6dfa6ac1c5b91b4.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>茅家埠，西湖边没那么热闹却依然保有西湖风景的景点<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/d11525e3856c02e9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>黛色参天,辅以太极八卦<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/72065ae89b5f238b.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>偶遇湖边的茅草亭<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/d7c17b35d05156f9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>斑驳的通利古桥，在一旁见证着岁月流逝<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/95446ce7505fbe54.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>西湖落日，伴有秋天大雁南飞<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/2c24a91f6386ef63.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>晚秋的西湖和断桥<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/9f952d2daf3bb9c9.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>深秋早晨的虎跑路，也是我的上班路，形色匆匆</p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/2019/05/20190522141559.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p>深秋的景区随拍<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/82da6bcc56722a35.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>深秋的西湖边，虽秋风肃杀，却挡不住远处的游人如织<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/2c81dfe74753fec4.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>纸币上的三潭印月了解一下<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/24b8af63d833fd1d.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>三潭映月岛上风光<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/1f78ee530a31b695.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/2f8bc528a5847f85.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>雪夜西湖边<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/b063d265aed740a2.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/3fad3f7368ffcf08.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p>雪夜的宝石山上<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/90cc5271ffcf6efb.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>二、西溪湿地，杭州的肺</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>大雪后的湿地，银装素裹<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/770af3e72f807775.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/b8354dea68aaec32.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>在冬日暖阳下的西溪湿地中，度过2016年的最后一天，见证着这一年最后的落日</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/268f892086787cd1.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="6"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/fb0847419cb20802.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>春日里，在西溪湿地泛舟，看河边的建筑，望船头的河道</li>
</ul>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="7"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1904/cbbf2ec58beba67f.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="8"><img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1904/96de7509a2ebc202.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<ul>
<li>
<p><strong>三、灵隐寺，杭州名刹</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>飞来峰口<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/af5e0f9d0fb0cb6b.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>理公之塔，底部覆钵、仰莲刹座，上承宝珠、宝瓶，集佛教史迹、造塔艺术、佛像雕刻于一体<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/f965221040e4f8bc.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>刻于山体上的多宝天王<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/784f3d46b9a74d2f.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>济公殿<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/4bfafcb06def5e4f.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>香火鼎盛的大雄宝殿<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/dabbccf2c8cea820.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>四、钱江新城，不仅仅是杭州新地标</strong></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>国庆节，向祖国母亲致敬<br>
<img src="https://wz-1255445901.file.myqcloud.com/picture/1809/8b0f2364faacdfd0.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
</li>
<li>
<p>大金球<br>
